##  How to Run

1. Clone the repository.
2. Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA.
3. Reload Maven dependencies.
4. Run the `App.java` file.

##  Learning Outcome

This project helped me understand the fundamentals of the Spring Framework, including Maven project configuration, Spring Bean creation, IoC (Inversion of Control), and Dependency Injection using XML-based configuration.
